      • ActionBar

        public static final int[] ActionBar
        ============================================ Attributes used to style the Action Bar. These should be set on your theme; the default actionBarStyle will propagate them to the correct elements as needed. Please Note: when overriding attributes for an ActionBar style you must specify each attribute twice: once with the "android:" namespace prefix and once without.

        Includes the following attributes:

        AttributeDescription
        com.appetizeapp.android:background Specifies a background drawable for the action bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:backgroundSplit Specifies a background drawable for the bottom component of a split action bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:backgroundStacked Specifies a background drawable for a second stacked row of the action bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:customNavigationLayout Specifies a layout for custom navigation.
        com.appetizeapp.android:displayOptions Options affecting how the action bar is displayed.
        com.appetizeapp.android:divider Specifies the drawable used for item dividers.
        com.appetizeapp.android:height Specifies a fixed height.
        com.appetizeapp.android:homeLayout Specifies a layout to use for the "home" section of the action bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:icon Specifies the drawable used for the application icon.
        com.appetizeapp.android:indeterminateProgressStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an indeterminate progress spinner.
        com.appetizeapp.android:itemPadding Specifies padding that should be applied to the left and right sides of system-provided items in the bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:logo Specifies the drawable used for the application logo.
        com.appetizeapp.android:navigationMode The type of navigation to use.
        com.appetizeapp.android:progressBarPadding Specifies the horizontal padding on either end for an embedded progress bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:progressBarStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an embedded progress bar.
        com.appetizeapp.android:subtitle Specifies subtitle text used for navigationMode="normal"
        com.appetizeapp.android:subtitleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for subtitle text.
        com.appetizeapp.android:title Specifies title text used for navigationMode="normal"
        com.appetizeapp.android:titleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for title text.
        See Also:
        ActionBar_background, ActionBar_backgroundSplit, ActionBar_backgroundStacked, ActionBar_customNavigationLayout, ActionBar_displayOptions, ActionBar_divider, ActionBar_height, ActionBar_homeLayout, ActionBar_icon, ActionBar_indeterminateProgressStyle, ActionBar_itemPadding, ActionBar_logo, ActionBar_navigationMode, ActionBar_progressBarPadding, ActionBar_progressBarStyle, ActionBar_subtitle, ActionBar_subtitleTextStyle, ActionBar_title, ActionBar_titleTextStyle
